title: Excessive Force
description:
Movie Description
Thomas Ian Griffith smashes his way into the top ranks of contemporary action heroes with this explosive thriller that delivers high-caliber action with &#039;Excessive Force.&#039;

Credits 
Cast: Thomas Ian Griffith 
Director: Jon Hess 

Synopsis
When $3 million in drug money disappears during an undercover bust, the mob begins executing the cops who they believe took the cash. But after they target Terry McCain&#039;s partners, the furious detective goes after the mob boss responsible -- using ever drop of his martial arts skills.
